{"markdown":{"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"::: navbar\n``` {=html}          \n<!-- Navbar -->\n<nav>\n  <a href=\"#\" class=\"nav-logo\">ion<span>data</span></a>\n  <ul class=\"nav-links\">\n    <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n  </ul>\n</nav>\n```\n:::\n\n::: header-background\n``` {=html}          \n<!-- HERO -->\n<section class=\"hero\">\n  <div class=\"hero-image\">\n    <img src=\"images/landing-img.jpg\" alt=\"Hands on a laptop keyboard with charts on screen\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"hero-content\">\n    <p class=\"hero-eyebrow\">Data science · Analysis · Visualisation</p>\n    <h1 class=\"hero-heading\">\n      A clear-eyed view on<br>\n      <em>how we got here</em><br>\n      and where we might go next\n    </h1>\n    <p class=\"hero-subtext\">iondata supports clients with rigorous data science solutions — from collection and analysis to visualisation and communication.</p>\n    <a href=\"#about\" class=\"hero-cta\">\n      Learn more\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\">\n        <path d=\"M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4\"/>\n      </svg>\n    </a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n```\n:::\n\n::: services-strip\n``` {=html}\n<!-- SERVICES STRIP -->\n<div class=\"services-strip\">\n  <div class=\"service-item\">\n    <div class=\"service-num\">01</div>\n    <div class=\"service-title\">Data collection</div>\n    <div class=\"service-desc\">Structured sourcing and cleaning of complex, multi-dimensional datasets.</div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"service-item\">\n    <div class=\"service-num\">02</div>\n    <div class=\"service-title\">Data analysis</div>\n    <div class=\"service-desc\">Rigorous statistical and econometric methods applied to real-world questions.</div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"service-item\">\n    <div class=\"service-num\">03</div>\n    <div class=\"service-title\">Visualisation & communication</div>\n    <div class=\"service-desc\">Presenting findings with clarity, precision, and visual impact.</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n\n::: histographiq-promo\n``` {=html}\n<!-- HISTOGRAPHIQ PROMO -->\n<div class=\"promo\">\n  <div>\n    <div class=\"promo-badge\">Recently launched</div>\n    <div class=\"promo-heading\">HistographIQ</div>\n    <div class=\"promo-sub\">Interactive maps with integrated timelines to visualise history.</div>\n  </div>\n  <a href=\"https://histographiq.com\" class=\"promo-link\">\n    Explore the app\n    <svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\">\n      <path d=\"M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4\"/>\n    </svg>\n  </a>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n\n``` {=html}   \n<section id=\"about\" class=\"about\">\n  <div class=\"about-left\">\n    <p class=\"section-label\">About</p>\n    <h2 class=\"section-heading\">Data science rooted in economics and real-world research</h2>\n    <div class=\"about-photo-wrap\">\n      <img src=\"images/myphoto.jpg\" alt=\"Michael Bratt\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"about-right\">\n    <div class=\"about-body\">\n      <p><strong>iondata</strong> serves clients with data science solutions to support their understanding and analysis of events, trends, and underlying currents. Services span the entire data science cycle — from data collection through analysis to visualisation and communication.</p>\n      <p>Michael Bratt is the founder of <strong>iondata</strong>. He started his career in international trade and economic development, including work at the Swedish <a href=\"https://www.kommerskollegium.se/en/\">National Board of Trade</a> and the <a href=\"https://unctad.org/\">UN Trade and Development (UNCTAD)</a>.</p>\n      <p>His more recent work has focused on the calculation and analysis of country and city rankings on issues related to talent, finance, and technology. Recent projects include the <a href=\"https://fcci.webflow.io\">Financial Centres Competitiveness Index</a>, supported by Stern at NYU Abu Dhabi, and the <a href=\"https://citiesfuturereadinessindex.net\">Cities Future Readiness Index</a>. Past projects include <a href=\"https://www.insead.edu/faculty-research/research/gtci\">The Global Talent Competitiveness Index</a> for INSEAD and the <a href=\"https://futurereadinessindex.com\">Future Readiness Economic Index</a> commissioned by Google.</p>\n      <p>Michael holds a PhD in Economics from the University of Geneva, where his research focused on <a href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/roie.12297\">the economic impact of non-tariff barriers to international trade</a>.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"work\" class=\"project-tags\">\n      <span class=\"project-tag\">Country rankings</span>\n      <span class=\"project-tag\">City indices</span>\n      <span class=\"project-tag\">International trade</span>\n      <span class=\"project-tag\">Econometrics</span>\n      <span class=\"project-tag\">Data visualisation</span>\n      <span class=\"project-tag\">Web apps</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<div class=\"ruled-divider\"><span>iondata · Switzerland</span></div>\n```\n\n\n``` {=html}         \n<!-- CONTACT -->\n<section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n  <div class=\"contact-left\">\n    <h2 class=\"contact-heading\">\n      Let's work<br><em>together</em>\n    </h2>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"contact-right\">\n    <div class=\"contact-detail\">\n      <span class=\"contact-detail-label\">Email</span>\n      <a href=\"mailto:info@iondata.co\">info@iondata.co</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"contact-detail\">\n      <span class=\"contact-detail-label\">GitHub</span>\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/mibratt/\">github.com/mibratt</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n```\n\n\n::: {#footer}\n``` {=html}\n<footer>\n  <div class=\"footer-logo\">ion<span>data</span></div>\n  <div class=\"footer-copy\">© 2025 iondata. All rights reserved.</div>\n</footer>\n```\n:::","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier